&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;The ideal candidate is customer-focused, highly organized, and passionate about education. This position requires strong leadership skills, problem-solving abilities, and the ability to manage multiple priorities in a fast-paced environment.&lt;/p&gt;
