&lt;li&gt;Monitor and maintain high customer service standards across all parent-facing interactions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure timely responses to phone calls, emails, WeChat messages, and other inquiries.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage student check-in/check-out procedures and attendance tracking.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Team Leadership&lt;/h3&gt;
