&lt;li&gt;Create staff schedules and ensure adequate front desk coverage during operating hours.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor team performance and provide coaching, feedback, and professional development support.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
